IMPORTANT NOTES
(Please read before ordering) 1. Any imperfections in the text or clipart shown in the “Your Design” box will be fixed prior to production. You will receive an Artwork Proof. For approval. 2. Any imperfections in the uploaded images may be fixed upon request for a nominal fee. Call for details. 3. All designs will be engraved into the foil and chocolate. 4. Side 2 is optional and will add a one-time fee of $29.00. 5. By choosing a different secondary color, you will get a mixture of both foil colors at no extra charge. Minimum of 100 coins per color. NEED HELP DESIGNING YOUR CHOCOLATE COINS?
Please call our Design Team at 1-866-230-7730 for help at no extra cost. PRODUCTION TIME:
Standard: 5-7 business days
Rush: 2-4 business days – Call 1-866-230-7730 to arrange for a rush order. Production time DOES NOT include shipping time.
